<item>
            <title>[CXF-8088] ensure jaxrs endpoint can work correctly when using a shared bus exposed from another bundle</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CXF-8088</link>
                <project id="12310511" key="CXF">CXF</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;major 2 issues&lt;br/&gt;
1. not unregister the jaxrs endpoint correctly when stop the jaxrs endpoint bundle.&lt;br/&gt;
2. jaxrs binding should be added as bus extension so that the bus used by jaxrs binding factory is always valid&lt;/p&gt;</description>
