                            <comment id="17008594" author="xldai" created="Mon, 6 Jan 2020 07:33:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=ffang&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;ffang&quot;&gt;ffang&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;br/&gt;
The changes seems introduce a regression in case of operate the JAXRSServerFactoryBean dynamically using blueprint configuration.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In blueprint.xml:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
    &amp;lt;jaxrs:server id=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;ARestService&quot;&lt;/span&gt; address=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;/sam&quot;&lt;/span&gt; &amp;gt;
        &amp;lt;jaxrs:serviceBeans&amp;gt;
            &amp;lt;ref component-id=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;restService&quot;&lt;/span&gt; /&amp;gt;
        &amp;lt;/jaxrs:serviceBeans&amp;gt;
        &amp;lt;jaxrs:providers&amp;gt;
            &amp;lt;bean class=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;org.apache.cxf.jaxrs.provider.json.JSONProvider&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;
                &amp;lt;property name=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;ignoreNamespaces&quot;&lt;/span&gt; value=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt; /&amp;gt;
                &amp;lt;property name=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;dropRootElement&quot;&lt;/span&gt; value=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt; /&amp;gt;
            &amp;lt;/bean&amp;gt;
        &amp;lt;/jaxrs:providers&amp;gt;
    &amp;lt;/jaxrs:server&amp;gt;
	
    &amp;lt;bean id=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;securityProvider&quot;&lt;/span&gt; class=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;org.abc.security.ServiceSecurityProvider&quot;&lt;/span&gt; init-method=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;init&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;
        &amp;lt;property name=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;serviceEndpoint&quot;&lt;/span&gt; ref=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;ARestService&quot;&lt;/span&gt; /&amp;gt;
    &amp;lt;/bean&amp;gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Adding some providers to the jaxrs:server dynamically in Java class:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;class &lt;/span&gt;ServiceSecurityProvider {
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;private&lt;/span&gt; JAXRSServerFactoryBean serviceEndpoint;

    &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; void setServiceEndpoint(JAXRSServerFactoryBean serviceEndpoint) {
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt;.serviceEndpoint = serviceEndpoint;
    }

    &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; void init() {
        Server oldServer = serviceEndpoint.getServer();
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (oldServer.isStarted()) {
        	oldServer.stop();
        	oldServer.destroy();
        }
		
        List&amp;lt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;Object&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt; providers = (List&amp;lt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;Object&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;) serviceEndpoint.getProviders();
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;//add some security providers dynamically depends on the configuration changes
&lt;/span&gt;        providers.add(xxx);

        Server newServer = serviceEndpoint.create();
        newServer.start();
    }
}
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Then the new Server couldn&apos;t be created properly with the expected providers in CXF 3.3.4.&lt;br/&gt;
But it worked well in CXF 3.3.1.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17010746" author="coheigea" created="Wed, 8 Jan 2020 14:57:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=xldai&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;xldai&quot;&gt;xldai&lt;/a&gt; I think the issue here is that your ServiceSecurityProvider needs to cast the JAXRSServerFactoryBean to BPJAXRSServerFactoryBean and call destroy before creating a new server.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
